gress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whenever any field in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property changes.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"}}}